text:
Hello!
I'll be in your care from today.

I'm Juri Saijo from HO-KA-GO CLIMAX GIRLS.
Nice to meet you!

Thank you very much for your kindness.
Likewise, I look forward to working with you.

As expected.
That was a polite introduction.

Anyway, there's something I want to
confirm about the schedule──

If the staff members are available,
I'd like to talk to them...

Oh, I see.
Then I'll reach out to them from my end.

Yeah, if I'm called upon,
I have to give it my all!
